We are a PKing, Skilling and Pvming server with a 100% GUARANTEED up-time status.
Are you looking for a server with NO LAG?
Are you looking for a server with an active wilderness?
Are you looking for a server with guarenteed updates at least twice a week?
Then CyberZ is the right place for you, it all starts here!
CyberZ is a new server and continues to grow on a daily basis.The server is growing rapidly and would love for YOU to join too!
CyberZ Features:
• 24/7 Active Skilling, PvMing and PKing
• Active forums
• Updates every other day guarenteed
• Excellent, professional, and dedicated staff
• A lot of server events
• Automatic daily lottery drawings
• Decent starter package
• Stable economy, no economy-resets
• Amazing donator benefits
• A awesome donator zone
• Vote Shop
• Fully working Highscores!
• TokHaar-Kal Cape, Comp Cape, Max Cape
• All PvP items, chaotics, nex sets, corrupts
• Working skills including Dungeoneering
• Slay points that can be gained from pking, slaying, etc..
• Slayer Point shop
• (::help) Which notifies our staff that someone needs help
• Working Teleblock

[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/hgqWPLF.png[/img] • Prestige Shop, every prestige you get a new cape to the store.

• The community has a voice and suggestion are being read by the higher ups
